name: Film
description:
I want to begin my series of works made on a film camera from this particular shot. Nothing lasts forever, as you might have noticed, and namely photos help us leave the moment, the emotion, the feeling in our memories. 
This is a picture of a couple that’s long gone. They live each other’s lives, love other people, think about different plans for the future, but this photo left in their hearts as a warm memory of each other and of the days when they were good together. 
Love and don’t be afraid to be alone!
